  "title": "Assistant Service Engineer [Jurong East | 5 days | up to $3200] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Assistant Service Engineer </strong></h3><p><strong>5 days, 8.30am- 6pm</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $3,000 - $3,200</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Penjuru Lane, Singapore 609189 (Jurong East)</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform preventive maintenance of production equipment.</li><li>To report in writing for maintenance carry out.</li><li>To ensure customer satisfaction at their premises.</li><li>Able to standby after office hours, when required, to provide support for urgent projects or to handle unexpected issues that may arise outside of regular business hours.</li><li>Perform ad-hoc duties assigned by supervisor.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/ITE/NTC in Electrical & Electronic or in relevant fields.</li><li>Must possess class 3 license.</li><li>Must understand basic AC & DC circuitry and electronic.</li><li>Experience in soldering / Assembly</li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
